Welcome Katherine\");\n        assertThat(mockingDetails(lifecycleRepository).isMock()).isTrue();\n        assertThat(lifecycleRepository).isNotSameAs(repository);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void mockitoSettingsCanMakeUnusedStubbingLenient() {"}]}
